$hr1 = random(11,24,1);
$min1 = $hr1*60;
$min2 = random(101,150,1);
$sec2 = $min2*60;

##############################################

BEGIN_PGML

Do the following unit conversions.

a. [`` [$hr1] \text{ hours} = ``] [__________]{$min1} [`` \text{ minutes} ``]

a. [`` [$sec2] \text{ seconds} = ``] [__________]{$min2} [`` \text{ minutes} ``]

END_PGML


